device,
which
could
be
activated
remotely
from
the
bank.
The
manager
had
only
used
the
emergency
system
once,
after
a
hijacking,
and
it
had
worked
flawlessly
locating
the
truck
and
transmitting
the
coordinates
to
the
authorities
automatically.
Tonight,
however,
the
manager
had
the
impression
the
president
was
hoping
for
a
bit
