prudence.
"Sir,
you
are
aware
that
if
I
activate
the
LoJack
system,
the
transponder
will
simultaneously
inform
the
authorities
that
we
have
a
problem."
Vernet
was
silent
for
several
seconds.
"Yes,
I
know.
Do
it
anyway.
Truck
number
three.
I'll
hold.
I
need
the
exact
location
of
that
truck
the
instant
you
have
